    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document catalogs a number of known problems with World Wide Web (WWW) (caching) proxies and cache servers.  The goal of the document is to provide a discussion of the problems and proposed workarounds, and ultimately to improve conditions by illustrating problems.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
